[I] A player for various audio formats

[T] XMP is a player for various PC and Amiga module formats including:
[T]
[T] XM MOD MOD M15 IT S3M STM STX MTM MTN IMF PTM MDL ULT MMD PTM DIGI
[T] EMOD OKT SFX FAR STIM KSM WN PM KRIS UNIC P60A PRU1 PRU2 PM01 PM10
[T] PM18 PM20 PM40 AC1D PP10 XANN ZEN NP DI MP 669 FNK AMD RAD CRB ALM

[U] https://xmp.sourceforge.net/

